<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head><meta charset='utf-8'></head>
  <body>
    <p>Hey <%= firstName %>,</p>
    <br>
    <p>
      How are you doing? I'm doing well. It's been like <%= numMonthsSinceContact %> months
      since we last talked. I'm learning to code full-time at Fullstack Academy and enjoying 
      my time.
    </p>
    <p>
      I've been blogging about my experiences at Fullstack on my blog. 
      Check out my latest posts: 
      <ul>
      <% for(var i = 0; i < latestPosts.length; i++) { %>
        <li><a href="<%= latestPosts[i].short_url %>"><%= latestPosts[i].title %></a></li>
      <% } %>
        <li><a href="http://codefishandchips.tumblr.com">My Blog</a></li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p>
      Talk soon,<br>
      Isaac
    </p>
  </body>
</html>

